Description: Accelerate your workoutYou like your day active, your workouts challenging, and your technology accurate and hassle free. Whether youre passionate about running, hiking, walking or just staying fit, HealthSense Smart Pedometer Watch PD 102 give you what you need, and you dont sacrifice accuracy for simplicity or features-you get them all! HealthSense Smart 3D pedometer watch PD 102 is designed with fitness in mind keeps track of every step while also providing a Calorie Counter, Exercise timer, Daily Alarm, Distance, Speed, Timer, Stopwatch, and Backlight functions. The slick, glossy finish and lightweight design keeps you stylish and comfortable, in and out of the gym. Smart 3D TechnologyThe HealthSense PD 102 is the world?s most advanced 3D pedometer watch. Unlike other pedometers that do not work accurately unless placed vertically, the HealthSense PD 102 Pedometer utilizes the latest generation in Tri-Axis technology to provide superior accuracy in any position, whether up, down, flat, on its side, or at any angle. Moreover, the PD 102 Pedometer utilizes a Digital 3D Acceleration Sensor which is far more accurate than mechanical sensors used in other pedometers PedometerHighly accurate step counter watch with adjustable accelerator to shuffle between running and walking, and can calculate your average speed, distance, caloric expenditure, and total exercise time etc.The PD 102 has a delayed step counter feature that differentiates between ancillary movements and actual steps. This feature provides users with the most accurate results by delaying calculation until it has registered 10 steps in a row to eliminate overly sensitive step counting. DesignHealthSense PD 102 strap is made up of soft, comfortable and waterproof polyurethane, and the case is a high quality polycarbonate that?s water resistant to 10 Meters!
